saturn-mojozork
================

This project is a Sega Saturn port of MojoZork by Ryan C. "Icculus" Gordon
(https://github.com/icculus/mojozork). It is an altered source version, plainly
marked as such in accordance with condition 2 of the license below. Saturn-specific
additions in this repository are Copyright (c) 2026 Suinevere and are released under
the same terms.

The Z-Machine version 3 story files bundled under `saturn/cd/data/Z3/` are Infocom's
games and are NOT covered by the license below; they carry their own licensing —
see `saturn/game-licenses/`.

Third-party components used via git submodule (e.g. SaturnRingLib) retain their own
licenses in their own repositories.

